"{\"uid\": \"theadvocate.com.au-story-8722976-stewart-mcsweyn-reaches-5000m-olympic-final-after-appeal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A successful appeal following a tumultuous heat of the 5000-metres has given Stewart McSweyn a second chance at Olympic glory.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 77, \"end\": 92, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_McSweyn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stewart McSweyn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_McSweyn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stewart_McSweyn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  The 29-year-old King Islander will run in the 5000-metre final despite finishing three seconds outside the top eight at Stade de France.\", \"from\": 128, \"to\": 300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 180, \"end\": 184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"score\": 0.9623159249470815, \"rank\": 0.03815145475224404, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\"}, {\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain's George Mills caused three runners to fall in the final straight, while forcing McSweyn onto the infield, but he kept his feet and finished the race in 12thwith a time of 14:12.31.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9953548919083981, \"rank\": 0.004661876914135603, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy I stayed up.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of guys hit the ground, so we will see what happens,\\\" McSweyn said in the aftermath.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't able to finish the race how I hoped, but I guess we have got to wait and see what the officials make of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McSweyn later appealed the result - and the jury agreed - advancing him to the next round several hours later.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Four other runners that were also caught up in the chaos have also been advanced, meaning 22 athletes will contest the final on Sunday, August 11 at 3.50am.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be McSweyn's second appearance in an Olympic final after finishing seventh in the 1500 meters at the Tokyo Olympics in 2021.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is the only Australian to qualify for the 5000-metre final after Morgan McDonald contested the second heat and agonisingly missed out in ninth spot by 0.05 seconds.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_McDonald\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Morgan McDonald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_McDonald\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_McDonald\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was part of a somewhat farcical day, which included a cameraman wandering onto the track while racing took place.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports journalist at The Advocate on Tasmania's North-West Coast.\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1